rows.label: bf07400100_0020
rows.name:
What's wrong?
You've been silent ever since the enemies disappeared.

rows.label: bf07400100_0090
rows.name:
Why?
Why did it become so worn out?

rows.label: bf07400100_0100
rows.name: Had its core already decayed away?

rows.label: bf07400100_0110
rows.name:
What the hell?
What did we come all this way for?

rows.label: bf07400100_0130
rows.name:
How can it be okay?
Homura's one true sword just broke!

rows.label: bf07400100_0140
rows.name:
What we really need
is not something like a sword.

rows.label: bf07400100_0160
rows.name: It's fine. I won't lose anymore.

rows.label: bf07400100_0170
rows.name: Let's go rescue Homura and Hikari.

rows.label: bf07400100_0210
rows.name: You've realized something, haven't you, Rex?

rows.label: bf07400100_0220
rows.name: It's something beyond our understanding, isn't it?

rows.label: bf07400100_0230
rows.name:
I'm with you.
I've seen that look in your eyes before.
